{"data":[{"date":"07:13 09/08","title":"CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/clb-thai-son-nam-lap-ky-tich-o-giai-vo-dich-futsal-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Futsal Vi\u1ec7t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Nagoya Oceans \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i c\u00e1c CLB m\u1ea1nh ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</h2><h2>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 3-2 Nagoya Oceans\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/9/Nagoya-Oceans-2-3-Thai-Son-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB futsal Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00e1c CLB m\u1ea1nh ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nagoya Oceans.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u1ed3 V\u0103n \u00dd. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Minh Tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam sau nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Tin-HOT-bong-da-toi-8-8-Modric-tro-lai-tap-luyen-du-doi-roi-Real-tsn-660-1533735575-629-width660height490.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vui s\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a CLB futsal t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nagoya Oceans l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai futsal Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ed1c futsal Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, tuy\u1ec3n futsal Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua tuy\u1ec3n futsal Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 World Cup Futsal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang l\u00e0 Bank of Beirut c\u1ee7a Lebanon, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Chonburi Bluewave c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c: Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 3-2 Nagoya Oceans<br>\r\nGhi b\u00e0n<br>\r\nTh\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam: Minh Tr\u00ed 18, 21', V\u0103n \u00dd 44'<br>\r\nNagoya Oceans: Ando 6', Nishitani 20'<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5270","checkdouble":"194071"},{"date":"08:44 09/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song G\u0110 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"u23 thai lan\" title=\"u23 th\u00e1i lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/dt-olympic-thai-lan-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-asiad.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i k\u00ec v\u1ecdng \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &lsquo;Messi Th\u00e1i&rsquo;, Chanathip Songkrasin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u0129 thu\u1eadt L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT), \u00f4ng Witthaya Laohakul v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2014, v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m to\u00e0n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23. T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Olympic Uzbekistan, Olympic Qatar v\u00e0 Olympic Bangladesh. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Qatar v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-thai-lan-loai-mot-loat-cau-thu-sau-that-bai-tai-myanmar-168-193860.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i Lan lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar-168-193796.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar-168-193796.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i  Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nU23 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5269","checkdouble":"194075"},{"date":"08:03 09/08","title":"Sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1ec1 ch\u1ebft \u201cchi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d c\u00f9ng Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0 ch\u1ebft ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Thibaut Courtois.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nReal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Courtois</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thibaut Courtois. Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Courtois s\u1ebd sang ch\u01a1i cho Real theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i, Los Blancos s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m. Sau bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c, Courtois s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (9/8) t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNavas quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Real nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua l\u00e0 Keylor Navas nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n thay tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Levante n\u0103m 2014, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n Navas \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft t\u1ed1t. Anh c\u00f9ng B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 1 La Liga c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Keylor Navas ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nghi\u00eam t\u00fac r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i th\u00e0 ch\u1ebft c\u00f2n h\u01a1n&rdquo;, Navas n\u00f3i tr\u00ean ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Onda Cero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-chi-tiet-hop-dong-courtois-sap-ky-voi-real-madrid-172-194030.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Courtois s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Real Madrid?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan-180-193950.html\">V\u00ec &ldquo;mi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh&rdquo; b\u00e9o b\u1edf n\u00e0y, Modric t\u00ednh b\u1ecf Real sang Inter</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5268","checkdouble":"194072"},{"date":"08:36 09/08","title":"Barca c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/23/barca-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-mignolet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Barca.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mignolet \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Simon Mignolet th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 cho Rakirus. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, The Kop b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mua anh v\u1ec1 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Barca, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Barca, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/Vuot-mat-Barca,-Napoli-muon-mua-Simon-Mignolet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Mignolet mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMignolet l\u00fac n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, sau Karius v\u00e0 Alisson. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. \u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i \u1edf Anfield, c\u1ef1u sao Sunderland \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Mignolet ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, Liverpool c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. The Kop mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Napoli quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Simon Mignolet</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool-180-192432.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Barca h\u1ecfi mua Simon Mignolet</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 thay th\u1ebf Jasper Cillessen, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i do kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu thanh Mignolet co kha nang can pha phat den rat tot.\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Mignolet c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/16/barca-chi-11-trieu-bang-mua-cai-ten-khong-the-ngo-toi-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli h\u1ecfi mua Mignolet&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Simon Mignolet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Italia, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Napoli \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Mignolet y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Liverpool song c\u1ef1u sao Sunderland v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Serie A.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5267","checkdouble":"194076"},{"date":"08:41 09/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Real Madrid t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/sao-tre-real-madrid-tu-tin-se-bung-no-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui. Sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ceballos kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDani Ceballos chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real Madrid t\u1eeb Real Betis v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i La Liga. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb HLV Zinedine Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Ceballos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Zidane v\u00e0 Julen Lopetegui l\u00ean thay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n. Ceballos xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Real t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Dani-Ceballos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dani Ceballos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nT\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Ceballos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin chi\u1ebfm 80% b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Ch\u00ednh Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi Real, Ceballos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Real Betis. Ngo\u00e0i 1 m\u00f9a ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 Andalusia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 64 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i La Liga 2 m\u00f9a 2015/16 v\u00e0 2016/17.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-khong-muon-so-sanh-bale-va-ronaldo-180-194028.html\">HLV Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n so s\u00e1nh Bale v\u00e0 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-truoc-mua-201819-dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon-180-194020.html\">Real th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 Juventus v\u00e0 Roma: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid-180-194072.html\">Sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1ec1 ch\u1ebft &ldquo;chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; c\u00f9ng Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5266","checkdouble":"194078"},{"date":"07:28 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/1/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00eda Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Courtois cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, vi\u1ec7c Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Courtois</span> tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Kovacic ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u00f9 Kovacic c\u00f3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5y th\u00ec The Blues c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch g\u00ec gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/CHINH-THUC-Tien-ve-Kovacic-gia-nhap-Chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc trao cho Kovacic m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh N&rsquo;golo Kante v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Jorginho \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League n\u0103m nay b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield. V\u00e0 HLV Sarri k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea3 hai t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 Kovacic v\u00e0 Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Kepa. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi ra t\u1edbi 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Bilbao nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf Courtois.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea l\u1ed7 n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i Courtois - Kovacic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kovacic t\u1eeb Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua \u0111\u1ee9t Kovacic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay Kovacic m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 24 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i Chelsea s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Kovacic n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Real trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-don-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194065.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5265","checkdouble":"194070"},{"date":"08:22 09/08","title":"Chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng, t\u1ea1i sao Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Rugani?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00f9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y thay cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte, HLV Maurizio Sarri quy\u1ebft th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Sau khi mang v\u1ec1 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia quy\u1ebft t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Daniele Rugani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Rugani t\u1eebng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng Sarri 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013/14 v\u00e0 2014/15 t\u1ea1i Empoli. Sau \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus song su\u1ed1t 3 n\u0103m qua v\u1eabn ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rugani n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAi c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Juventus s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Rugani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Leonardo Bonucci t\u1eeb AC Milan, Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u1edbn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2u, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u1eef v\u1eefng l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ch\u00ednh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi dam mua Rugani\" title=\"Arsenal chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rugani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Juventus kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Rugani, h\u1ecd h\u00e9t m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi tr\u1ea3&rdquo;, Torchia n\u00f3i v\u1edbi RMC Sport. &ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. L\u1eafng nghe m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Turin. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1edbn, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng Juventus \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Rugani c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-sap-den-chelsea-172-194055.html\">Ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t Courtois, Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\">N\u00f3ng: Athletic Bilbao x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Kepa Arrizabalaga s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5264","checkdouble":"194073"},{"date":"08:36 09/08","title":"H\u1ecdc Mourinho, Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/sanchez-yeu-cau-mu-chieu-mo-them-sieu-sao.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sanchez cho r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Sanchez mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, HLV Jose Mourinho v\u1eabn mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Harry Maguire, Jerome Boateng v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sanchez y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam si\u00eau sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/sanchez-yeu-cau-mu-chieu-mo-them-sieu-sao.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Sanchez cho r\u1eb1ng Man United c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch n\u1ed5 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d. Theo ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Arturo Vidal l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 MU c\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u1ede Man United, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Barcelona m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Vidal, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Chile.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTheo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 t\u00f4i quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, Fred l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n lao l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n d\u00e2ng cao. V\u00e0 theo t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Sanchez t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Old Trafford sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Sanchez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Premier League n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Khi b\u1ea1n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong 6 th\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m quen c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-thay-the-luke-shaw-172-194037.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay th\u1ebf Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5263","checkdouble":"194074"},{"date":"08:48 09/08","title":"PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jerome Boateng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U v\u00ec Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u00f2i 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 M.U chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Bild c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho-172-194013.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU</span>, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng HLV Jose Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u1edf Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBoateng \u0111ang \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich, song anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 38 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern Munich ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern chi ban Boateng voi gia 50 trieu bang\" title=\"Bayern ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Boateng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Boateng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 PSG d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra c\u00f2n k\u00e9m 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Bayern, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Boateng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Boateng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ngo\u00e0i trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Bayern, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5262","checkdouble":"194077"},{"date":"23:35 08/08","title":"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A CHINH TH\u1ee8C \u0111\u1ed5i sang logo m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n khi chia tay logo c\u0169 sang th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu m\u1edbi mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean Serie A nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn ngh\u0129. L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh khi Serie A h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Premier League v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1c CLB b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/co-cristiano-ronaldo-serie-a-doi-logo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo nh\u1eb1m t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Serie A c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c g\u00f3i ba n\u0103m gi\u1ed1ng Premier League. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Serie A \u0111\u1ed5i logo m\u1edbi theo h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o ch\u1eef \"A\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Serie A c\u0169ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi tr\u00ean Facebook, Instagram v\u00e0 Twitter, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u00ean \"SerieA\". Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng h\u01a1n h\u01a1n 1.2 tri\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Serie A t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \"xu\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1\". Ch\u1eef A trong logo m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \"Appassionante, Avvincente, Adrenalinica\" - t\u1ea1m d\u1ecbch \"th\u00fa v\u1ecb, h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, b\u01a1m Adrenaline\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Logo cu cua Serie A.\" title=\"Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/serie-a-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Logo c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Serie A k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng logo m\u1edbi b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \"khao kh\u00e1t t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ednh trung t\u00e2m cho ch\u1eef A\", c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \"m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta\". Vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i logo Serie A c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Italia nh\u01b0 Coppa Italia, Si\u00eau C\u00fap Italia v\u00e0 Primavera.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi, t\u1ea1o ra t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c quan, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n g\u1ed3m l\u00e1 c\u1edd Italia, m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u1eef A, t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi TIM\" - Tr\u00edch t\u1eeb th\u00f4ng c\u00e1o b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Serie A 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-nhan-xet-cristiano-ronaldo-den-serie-a-176-193919.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao-176-193834.html\">M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/liverpool-vs-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-193724.html\">Liverpool 5-0 Napoli: The Klopp h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A trong ng\u00e0y Alisson ra m\u1eaft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a-176-192603.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-khi-sao-serie-a-la-mieng-pizza-trong-mat-cac-dai-gia-nha-172-192560.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Khi sao Serie A l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng pizza trong m\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/sieu-sao-ronaldo-giup-juventus-pha-ky-luc-tren-youtube-188-192551.html\">Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo gi\u00fap Juventus ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean YouTube</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5261","checkdouble":"194058"},{"date":"22:54 08/08","title":"Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/loai-van-lam-hlv-park-hang-seo-da-noi-gi-voi-thu-mon-nay.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ri\u00eang v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y?\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park b\u1edfi \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng 3 su\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i U23 cho tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mang t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn cho ch\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Tien-Dung-khong-bang-Dang-Van-Lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 mong V\u0103n L\u00e2m th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ri\u00eang v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi an \u1ee7i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 di\u1ec5n ra trong 10 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung xoay quanh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn ai, b\u1ecf ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u00e2m khi \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c chia s\u1ebb \u00f4ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft b\u1edfi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u201cqu\u00e1 m\u1ecfng\u201d. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ebfn AFF Cup 2018 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay, khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa, V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u01a1i b\u1edbt n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay khi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 AFF Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chia tay V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 bay v\u00e0o B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, n\u01a1i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u00ed h\u1eadu, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Indonesia. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi bi\u1ebft tin b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad-472-194022.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD</span><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dang-van-lam-bi-loai-bat-ngo-nhung-hop-ly-472-193976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/Tien-Dung-khong-bang-Dang-Van-Lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/dang-van-lam-bi-loai-bat-ngo-nhung-hop-ly-472-193976.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Asiad 2018: B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u00eat Nam \u2013 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5260","checkdouble":"194057"},{"date":"00:37 09/08","title":"Sao HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/sao-hagl-noi-gi-khi-bi-loai-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 10 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i song anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Tien-ve-Minh-Vuong-noi-mot-dieu-sau-khi-bi-loai-khoi-DT-Olympic-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i do anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman v\u1eeba qua. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 anh h\u00e0o, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sa khi bi\u1ebft tin m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n, song anh c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \"C\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m cho t\u00f4i. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n. Xin ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\". <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 qu\u00ea Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i U23. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Xem ch\u1eebng Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn qu\u00e1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u U23 khi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh tham gia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5259","checkdouble":"194060"},{"date":"20:21 08/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 8/8: \"Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-toi-88-man-utd-can-them-2-tan-binh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\"Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh\", BLV Quang Huy nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 8/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Arsenal, Jens Lehmann nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Arsene Wenger, HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League trong s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 88 Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 88 Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Diem-tin-toi-88-Man-Utd-can-them-2-tan-binh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Rooney nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wayne Rooney kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u1ee7a Man Utd m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Real Madrid \u0111ang d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Luka Modric. Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia loan tin Inter \u0111ang t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Kim Hak-bum c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock out, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00f4ng s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung-min trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olivier Giroud ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Fekir ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lyon v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Moussa Wague v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 4.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 90 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 13 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Senegal v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u00e2u Phi ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bi quan c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos, Dani Ceballos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo ra \u0111i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Viec Van Quyet du ASIAD 2018 gay nhieu tranh cai.\" title=\"Vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/IMG_1147.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wolverhampton \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Adama Traore t\u1eeb Middlesbrough v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Wolverhampton m\u1edbi l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Everton trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/8 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), s\u1edbm h\u01a1n ba tu\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u1ee3i l\u00ean ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB khi\u1ebfn G\u0110\u0110H Premier League, Richard Scudamore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed1i 8/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-tottenham-truoc-mua-giai-201819-nguy-co-vang-khoi-top-4-172-194053.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: Nguy c\u01a1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi Top 4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-athletic-bilbao-xac-nhan-kepa-arrizabalaga-sap-den-chelsea-172-194052.html\">N\u00f3ng: Athletic Bilbao x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Kepa Arrizabalaga s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/david-luiz-ung-ho-chelsea-mua-kepa-voi-gia-ky-luc-172-194049.html\">Chelsea chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c mua Kepa, David Luiz n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lo-dau-hieu-cho-thay-kovacic-sap-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194048.html\">L\u1ed9 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Kovacic s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/kepa-arrizabalaga-co-du-kha-nang-thay-the-vi-tri-do-courtois-de-lai-172-194047.html\">Kepa Arrizabalaga \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/jose-mourinho-va-manchester-united-mua-bong-moi-ao-mong-cuoi-cung-392-194046.html\">Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Manchester United m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi: \u1ea2o m\u1ed9ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5258","checkdouble":"194054"}]}